In selecting specific equipment, you should be concerned with the life of the battery, the capacity of the memory, the quality and type of audio output, and of course the user-friendly nature of the operation.
If music is a background setting for you and you are only going to listen to it for a short time, perhaps in the tram, any cell phone which plays MP3 is enough.
