From the perspective of customers, we consider this to be the most beneficial.
Vodafone's main strategy in this area is to find a partner for the construction of a shared network for fast mobile Internet.
Responsible authorities - buddy-buddy with operators
The procedure of the mobile operators is easy to understand, the entry of another operator would lead to increased competition, which would lead to lower prices and consequently to decrease their profits.
Why do we make this easy for such a competitor?
The tug of war around the creation of U:fon attests to the fact that when something is important to the operators, they can pull for the same team.
The most important pressure on the Czech Telecommunication Office was during the time of the creation of U:fon by T-Mobile.
Information available on the Czech Telecommunication Office's website attests to this.
